<h1>Problem 950 - 2014 IMOSL, A4</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 7</h2>
<p>Determine all functions \(f: \mathbb{Z}\to\mathbb{Z}\) satisfying
\[f\big(f(m)+n\big)+f(m)=f(n)+f(3m)+2014\]
for all integers \(m\) and \(n\).</p>
